title: Car Ride Conversation with #60SecClub Winner
description: So if you don't know, those that comment on my Instagram posts in the first 60 seconds are eligible for prizes and exclusive access from me. Anything from swag, signed books, meetings, interviews, and anything above and in between is up for grabs. If you're not part of it, make sure you turn on my notifications !! In this soundbite the incredible Eva, who's a #60SecClub winner takes a ride with me to have our meeting. In this chat we talk angel investing, scaling a career, being patient, and something you've NEVER heard from me ... Make sure you listen to find out !
